{"id":193,"parent_id":191,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":193,"title":"Colossians 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Col.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The fulness of the Godhead dwells in Christ—Beware of being deceived by the traditions of men—The handwriting against us was nailed to the cross of Christ."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.1","order":"03.14.002.21062"},["b","1"],"For I would that ye knew what great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"conflict"],"I have for you, and",["i","for"],"them at",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Laodicea"],", and",["i","for"],"as many as have not seen my face in the flesh;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.2","order":"03.14.002.21063"},["b","2"],"That their hearts might be comforted, being knit together in love, and unto all riches of the full assurance of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"understanding"],", to the acknowledgement of the mystery of God,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"and"],"of the Father, and of Christ;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.3","order":"03.14.002.21064"},["b","3"],"In whom are hid all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"treasures"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"wisdom"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.4","order":"03.14.002.21065"},["b","4"],"And this I say, lest any man should beguile you with enticing words."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.5","order":"03.14.002.21066"},["b","5"],"For though I be absent in the flesh, yet am I with you in the spirit, joying and beholding your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"order"],", and the steadfastness of your faith in Christ."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.6","order":"03.14.002.21067"},["b","6"],"As ye have therefore received Christ Jesus the Lord,",["i","so"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"walk"],"ye in him:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.7","order":"03.14.002.21068"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Rooted"],"and built up in him, and stablished in the faith, as ye have been taught, abounding therein with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8","order":"03.14.002.21069"},["b","8"],"Beware lest any man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"spoil"],"you through",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"philosophy"],"and vain",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"deceit"],", after the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"tradition"],"of men, after the rudiments of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"world"],", and not after Christ."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.9","order":"03.14.002.21070"},["b","9"],"For in him dwelleth all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"fulness"],"of the Godhead bodily."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.10","order":"03.14.002.21071"},["b","10"],"And ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"complete"],"in him, which is the head of all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"principality"],"and power:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.11","order":"03.14.002.21072"},["b","11"],"In whom also ye are circumcised with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"circumcision"],"made without hands, in putting off the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"body"],"of the sins of the flesh by the circumcision of Christ:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.12","order":"03.14.002.21073"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Buried"],"with him in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"baptism"],", wherein also ye are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"risen"],"with",["i","him"],"through the faith of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"operation"],"of God, who hath raised him from the dead."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.13","order":"03.14.002.21074"},["b","13"],"And you, being dead in your sins and the uncircumcision of your flesh, hath he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"quickened together"],"with him, having forgiven you all trespasses;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.14","order":"03.14.002.21075"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Blotting"],"out the handwriting of ordinances that was against us, which was contrary to us, and took it out of the way, nailing it to his cross;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.15","order":"03.14.002.21076"},["b","15"],["i","And"],"having spoiled principalities and powers, he made a shew of them openly, triumphing over them in it."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.16","order":"03.14.002.21077"},["b","16"],"Let no man therefore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"judge"],"you in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"meat"],", or in drink, or in respect of an holyday, or of the new moon, or of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"sabbath"],["i","days:"]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.17","order":"03.14.002.21078"},["b","17"],"Which are a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"shadow"],"of things to come; but the body",["i","is"],"of Christ."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.18","order":"03.14.002.21079"},["b","18"],"Let no man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"beguile"],"you of your reward in a voluntary",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"humility"],"and worshipping of angels, intruding into those things which he hath not seen, vainly puffed up by his fleshly mind,"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.19","order":"03.14.002.21080"},["b","19"],"And not holding the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Head"],", from which all the body by joints and bands having nourishment ministered, and knit together, increaseth with the increase of God."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.20","order":"03.14.002.21081"},["b","20"],"Wherefore if ye be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"dead"],"with Christ from the rudiments of the world, why, as though living in the world, are ye subject to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"ordinances"],","],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.21","order":"03.14.002.21082"},["b","21"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"(Touch"],"not; taste not; handle not;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.22","order":"03.14.002.21083"},["b","22"],"Which all are to perish with the using;) after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"commandments"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"doctrines"],"of men?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.23","order":"03.14.002.21084"},["b","23"],"Which things have indeed a shew of wisdom in will worship, and humility, and neglecting of the body; not in any honour to the satisfying of the flesh."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.1a","order":"03.14.002.21085"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"anguish."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.1b","order":"03.14.002.21087"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.15.12-16"},"Col. 4:15 (12–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.11"},"Rev. 1:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.2a","order":"03.14.002.21089"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"TG Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.2b","order":"03.14.002.21091"},["b","2b"],["span.small","JST"],"Col. 2:2 …",["i","and of Christ, who is of God, even the Father;"]],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.3a","order":"03.14.002.21093"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.3b","order":"03.14.002.21095"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.7.6-7"},"1 Cor. 2:7 (6–7)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-intelligence-of"},"TG God, Intelligence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.3c","order":"03.14.002.21097"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"TG Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.5a","order":"03.14.002.21099"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/order"},"TG Order"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.6a","order":"03.14.002.21101"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.7a","order":"03.14.002.21103"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/3.17"},"Eph. 3:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.7b","order":"03.14.002.21105"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8a","order":"03.14.002.21107"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.9"},"Heb. 13:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8b","order":"03.14.002.21109"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12"},"D&C 123:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/learn"},"TG Learn"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8c","order":"03.14.002.21111"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deceit"},"TG Deceit"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/education"},"Education"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fraud"},"Fraud"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8d","order":"03.14.002.21113"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/traditions-of-men"},"TG Traditions of Men"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8e","order":"03.14.002.21115"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"TG Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.9a","order":"03.14.002.21117"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-relationships-with-the-father"},"TG Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.10a","order":"03.14.002.21119"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.16"},"John 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.10b","order":"03.14.002.21121"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.16"},"Col. 1:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/3.22"},"1 Pet. 3:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.11a","order":"03.14.002.21123"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.11b","order":"03.14.002.21125"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.6"},"Rom. 6:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.12a","order":"03.14.002.21127"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-memory"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Memory"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.12b","order":"03.14.002.21129"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-immersion"},"Baptism, Immersion"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.12c","order":"03.14.002.21131"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.1"},"Col. 3:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.12d","order":"03.14.002.21133"},["b","12d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/1.19.19-20"},"Eph. 1:19 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.13a","order":"03.14.002.21135"},["b","13a"],["span.small","GR"],"caused to become alive.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.14a","order":"03.14.002.21137"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/2.15"},"Eph. 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.16a","order":"03.14.002.21139"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.3.1-3"},"Rom. 14:3 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.16b","order":"03.14.002.21141"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/word-of-wisdom"},"TG Word of Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.16c","order":"03.14.002.21143"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.17a","order":"03.14.002.21145"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.18a","order":"03.14.002.21147"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.4.4-5"},"Matt. 24:4 (4–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.6"},"Mosiah 26:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12"},"D&C 123:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.18b","order":"03.14.002.21149"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.19a","order":"03.14.002.21151"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.15.15-16"},"Eph. 4:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.20a","order":"03.14.002.21153"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.5.2-5"},"Rom. 6:5 (2–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.3"},"Col. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.20b","order":"03.14.002.21155"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.21a","order":"03.14.002.21157"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-col/2.21-22"},["span.small","JST"],"Col. 2:21–22 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.22a","order":"03.14.002.21159"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/1.14"},"Titus 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7"},"D&C 46:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19"},"JS—H 1:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.22b","order":"03.14.002.21161"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.9"},"Matt. 15:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.9"},"2 Ne. 28:9"],"."]]}
